item.title: My First Pull Request
item.description: For those of you who know me and those of you who don’t, it won’t come as a surprise that I’m not a developer and I will never claim to be one. So, when I decided I wanted to learn how to contribute to a project on GitHub what better way to do this than to write a blog post about it.
